10. Install MySQL Client
11. Install MySQL Client
12. Connect and Manage Your Database


Creating and changing users
CREATE USER 'theuser'@'%' IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY 'thepassword';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'theuser'@'%' WITH GRANT OPTION;
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

---------Always Allocate Elastic IP address------
Go to EC2 Dashboard
Make ELastic IP Address
Associate IP address to Instance

